d chronosuit\", \"from\": 399, \"to\": 421}, {\"ngram\": \"the common parlance\", \"from\": 442, \"to\": 461}, {\"ngram\": \"the public\", \"from\": 488, \"to\": 498}, {\"ngram\": \"the first time\", \"from\": 503, \"to\": 517}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The brand says the suit is 'completely bespoke to athletes on the road to Paris 24'.\", \"from\": 521, \"to\": 605, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The brand\", \"from\": 521, \"to\": 530}, {\"ngram\": \"the suit\", \"from\": 536, \"to\": 544}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 571, \"to\": 579}, {\"ngram\": \"the road\", \"from\": 583, \"to\": 591}, {\"ngram\": \"Paris\", \"from\": 595, \"to\": 600}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We assume the skinsuit has been provided to Assos athletes or sponsored teams for some time but is now being made available to purchase via the brand's website.\", \"from\": 606, \"to\": 766, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the skinsuit\", \"from\": 616, \"to\": 628}, {\"ngram\": \"Assos athletes\", \"from\": 650, \"to\": 664}, {\"ngram\": \"sponsored teams\", \"from\": 668, \"to\": 683}, {\"ngram\": \"some time\", \"from\": 688, \"to\": 697}, {\"ngram\": \"the brand's website\", \"from\": 746, \"to\": 765}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The skinsuit, which is named the Fenoq, will be available as a single suit starting at \\u00a32,180 / $2,761.\", \"from\": 768, \"to\": 871, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The skinsuit\", \"from\": 768, \"to\": 780}, {\"ngram\": \"the Fenoq\", \"from\": 797, \"to\": 806}, {\"ngram\": \"a single suit\", \"from\": 829, \"to\": 842}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Or as a 'pack' which includes a 100% custom garment and includes overshoes.\", \"from\": 872, \"to\": 947, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a 'pack\", \"from\": 878, \"to\": 885}, {\"ngram\": \"a 100% custom garment\", \"from\": 902, \"to\": 923}, {\"ngram\": \"overshoes\", \"from\": 937, \"to\": 946}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The starting price for this option will be a whopping \\u00a35,670/ $7,040 On the Fenoq page on the brand's website, two suit options are listed.\", \"from\": 948, \"to\": 1088, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The starting price\", \"from\": 948, \"to\": 966}, {\"ngram\": \"this option\", \"from\": 971, \"to\": 982}, {\"ngram\": \"the Fenoq page\", \"from\": 1020, \"to\": 1034}, {\"ngram\": \"the brand's website\", \"from\": 1038, \"to\": 1057}, {\"ngram\": \"two suit options\", \"from\": 1059, \"to\": 1075}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The first is the Feno suit which is custom-made and designed for Time Trial use.\", \"from\": 1089, \"to\": 1169, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1154, \"end\": 1164, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Time_trial\", \"score\": 0.9019009418271391, \"rank\": 0.10876921580102675, \"text\": \"Time Trial\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Time_trial\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Time_trial\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Feno suit\", \"from\": 1102, \"to\": 1115}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Assos says the suit has been engineered and tested in the wind tunnel as well as at UCI WorldTour races.\", \"from\": 1170, \"to\": 1274, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1254, \"end\": 1257, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Union_Cycliste_Internationale\", \"score\": 0.9999996081670218, \"rank\": 3.9183297289283283e-07, \"text\": \"UCI\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Union_Cycliste_Internationale\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Union_Cycliste_Internationale\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Assos\", \"from\": 1170, \"to\": 1175}, {\"ngram\": \"the suit\", \"from\": 1181, \"to\": 1189}, {\"ngram\": \"the wind tunnel\", \"from\": 1224, \"to\": 1239}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We understand this option to be a highly optimised but off-the-peg skinsuit which starts at \\u00a32,710.\", \"from\": 1275, \"to\": 1374, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this option\", \"from\": 1289, \"to\": 1300}, {\"ngram\": \"the-peg\", \"from\": 1334, \"to\": 1341}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Fenoq pack jumps up in price and is a completely bespoke offering if you will, with the skinsuit itself being 100% custom.\", \"from\": 1376, \"to\": 1502, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Fenoq pack\", \"from\": 1376, \"to\": 1390}, {\"ngram\": \"price\", \"from\": 1403, \"to\": 1408}, {\"ngram\": \"a completely bespoke offering\", \"from\": 1416, \"to\": 1445}, {\"ngram\": \"the skinsuit\", \"from\": 1464, \"to\": 1476}, {\"ngram\": \"100% custom\", \"from\": 1490, \"to\": 1501}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Assos says the suit is wind tunnel data and track test certified.\", \"from\": 1503, \"to\": 1568, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Assos\", \"from\": 1503, \"to\": 1508}, {\"ngram\": \"the suit\", \"from\": 1514, \"to\": 1522}, {\"ngram\": \"wind tunnel data\", \"from\": 1526, \"to\": 1542}, {\"ngram\": \"track test\", \"from\": 1547, \"to\": 1557}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And that the fabric features a skinGrip finish, twinDeck sleeves and a back panel.\", \"from\": 1569, \"to\": 1651, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the fabric\", \"from\": 1578, \"to\": 1588}, {\"ngram\": \"a skinGrip finish\", \"from\": 1598, \"to\": 1615}, {\"ngram\": \"sleeves\", \"from\": 1626, \"to\": 1633}, {\"ngram\": \"a back panel\", \"from\": 1638, \"to\": 1650}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Overshoes are also included to the tune of \\u00a35,670 / $7,040There is not an option to add the skinsuit to your basket and purchase, instead interested customers are asked to fill out a form registering their interest.\", \"from\": 1652, \"to\": 1867, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Overshoes\", \"from\": 1652, \"to\": 1661}, {\"ngram\": \"the tune\", \"from\": 1683, \"to\": 1691}, {\"ngram\": \"an option\", \"from\": 1723, \"to\": 1732}, {\"ngram\": \"the skinsuit\", \"from\": 1740, \"to\": 1752}, {\"ngram\": \"your basket\", \"from\": 1756, \"to\": 1767}, {\"ngram\": \"purchase\", \"from\": 1772, \"to\": 1780}, {\"ngram\": \"instead interested customers\", \"from\": 1782, \"to\": 1810}, {\"ngram\": \"a form\", \"from\": 1833, \"to\": 1839}, {\"ngram\": \"their interest\", \"from\": 1852, \"to\": 1866}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The most cutting-edge, aero-optimised skinsuits still seem to be reserved for time trials and on the track, though race suits are commonplace on the road now.\", \"from\": 1871, \"to\": 2029, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The most cutting-edge\", \"from\": 1871, \"to\": 1892}, {\"ngram\": \"aero-optimised skinsuits\", \"from\": 1894, \"to\": 1918}, {\"ngram\": \"time trials\", \"from\": 1949, \"to\": 1960}, {\"ngram\": \"the track\", \"from\": 1968, \"to\": 1977}, {\"ngram\": \"race suits\", \"from\": 1986, \"to\": 1996}, {\"ngram\": \"the road\", \"from\": 2016, \"to\": 2024}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The fastest skin suits still take things one step further.\", \"from\": 2030, \"to\": 2088, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The fastest skin suits\", \"from\": 2030, \"to\": 2052}, {\"ngram\": \"things\", \"from\": 2064, \"to\": 2070}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Optimised and custom skin suits are nothing new but they are often not easy to find information on and difficult to purchase, especially when worn by national teams on the track for example.\", \"from\": 2090, \"to\": 2280, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Optimised and custom skin suits\", \"from\": 2090, \"to\": 2121}, {\"ngram\": \"nothing\", \"from\": 2126, \"to\": 2133}, {\"ngram\": \"information\", \"from\": 2174, \"to\": 2185}, {\"ngram\": \"national teams\", \"from\": 2240, \"to\": 2254}, {\"ngram\": \"the track\", \"from\": 2258, \"to\": 2267}, {\"ngram\": \"example\", \"from\": 2272, \"to\": 2279}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, for track races, any equipment used at the Olympic games must have been commercially available from January 1st of the Olympic year per UCI article 1.3.006, it's just not openly advertised as you might expect.\", \"from\": 2281, \"to\": 2499, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2426, \"end\": 2429, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Union_Cycliste_Internationale\", \"score\": 0.9999996081670218, \"rank\": 3.9183297289283283e-07, \"text\": \"UCI\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Union_Cycliste_Internationale\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Union_Cycliste_Internationale\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"track races\", \"from\": 2294, \"to\": 2305}, {\"ngram\": \"any equipment\", \"from\": 2307, \"to\": 2320}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic games\", \"from\": 2329, \"to\": 2346}, {\"ngram\": \"January 1st\", \"from\": 2390, \"to\": 2401}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic year\", \"from\": 2405, \"to\": 2421}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We would imagine if a nation thinks they have the fastest skinsuit around they are not likely to openly advertise it in the run-up to an Olympic year.\", \"from\": 2500, \"to\": 2650, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a nation\", \"from\": 2520, \"to\": 2528}, {\"ngram\": \"the fastest skinsuit\", \"from\": 2546, \"to\": 2566}, {\"ngram\": \"the run-up\", \"from\": 2620, \"to\": 2630}, {\"ngram\": \"an Olympic year\", \"from\": 2634, \"to\": 2649}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Some skinsuits have rocked the boat over the last few years and have even been rendered unusable thanks to shifting UCI regulations.\", \"from\": 2652, \"to\": 2784, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2768, \"end\": 2771, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Union_Cycliste_Internationale\", \"score\": 0.9999996081670218, \"rank\": 3.9183297289283283e-07, \"text\": \"UCI\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Union_Cycliste_Internationale\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Union_Cycliste_Internationale\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Some skinsuits\", \"from\": 2652, \"to\": 2666}, {\"ngram\": \"the boat\", \"from\": 2679, \"to\": 2687}, {\"ngram\": \"the last few years\", \"from\": 2693, \"to\": 2711}, {\"ngram\": \"unusable thanks\", \"from\": 2740, \"to\": 2755}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In 2022 we covered theVorteq skinsuit that Simon Yates usedto win a Giro TT stage.\", \"from\": 2785, \"to\": 2867, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2828, \"end\": 2839, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simon_Yates_(cyclist)\", \"score\": 0.9846717166986766, \"rank\": 0.015566340078741626, \"text\": \"Simon Yates\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simon_Yates_(cyclist)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simon_Yates_(cyclist)\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"theVorteq skinsuit\", \"from\": 2804, \"to\": 2822}, {\"ngram\": \"a Giro TT stage\", \"from\": 2851, \"to\": 2866}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That particular skinsuit was priced at \\u00a32,750 / $3,483 a little shy of the Assos Fenoq though Vorteq does list Paris Edition discipline-specific skinsuits starting from \\u00a33,000 / $3,800 The latest race content, interviews, features, reviews and expert buying guides, direct to your inbox!\", \"from\": 2868, \"to\": 3156, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2979, \"end\": 2984, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999849933, \"rank\": 1.485428985224417e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"That particular skinsuit\", \"from\": 2868, \"to\": 2892}, {\"ngram\": \"the Assos Fenoq\", \"from\": 2939, \"to\": 2954}, {\"ngram\": \"Vorteq\", \"from\": 2962, \"to\": 2968}, {\"ngram\": \"your inbox\", \"from\": 3144, \"to\": 3154}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Some skinsuits also fell foul of UCI rules several years ago, with thecontroversial Team Sky Castelli body paint skinsuitfeaturing 'vortex dimples' or grooved fabric to aid airflow falling outside of UCI regulations.\", \"from\": 3158, \"to\": 3374, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3191, \"end\": 3194, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Union_Cycliste_Internationale\", \"score\": 0.9999996081670218, \"rank\": 3.9183297289283283e-07, \"text\": \"UCI\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Union_Cycliste_Internationale\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Union_Cycliste_Internationale\"}, {\"begin\": 3242, \"end\": 3250, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ineos_Grenadiers\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Team Sky\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ineos_Grenadiers\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ineos_Grenadiers\"}, {\"begin\": 3251, \"end\": 3259, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leo_Castelli\", \"score\": 0.999986238843674, \"rank\": 1.376134257914877e-05, \"text\": \"Castelli\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leo_Castelli\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leo_Castelli\"}, {\"begin\": 3358, \"end\": 3361, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Union_Cycliste_Internationale\", \"score\": 0.9999996081670218, \"rank\": 3.9183297289283283e-07, \"text\": \"UCI\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Union_Cycliste_Internationale\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Union_Cycliste_Internationale\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Some skinsuits\", \"from\": 3158, \"to\": 3172}, {\"ngram\": \"grooved fabric\", \"from\": 3309, \"to\": 3323}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Endura / Drag 2 Zero skinsuit also fell outside the rules due to the 'textured material' the suit used.\", \"from\": 3375, \"to\": 3482, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3379, \"end\": 3385, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ford_Endura-D_engine\", \"score\": 0.9999999996953193, \"rank\": 1.1469618129205241e-10, \"text\": \"Endura\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ford_Endura-D_engine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ford_Endura-D_engine\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Drag 2 Zero skinsuit\", \"from\": 3388, \"to\": 3408}, {\"ngram\": \"the rules\", \"from\": 3427, \"to\": 3436}, {\"ngram\": \"the 'textured material\", \"from\": 3444, \"to\": 3466}, {\"ngram\": \"the suit\", \"from\": 3468, \"to\": 3476}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Other competitors to the Assos offering right now are perhaps the WattShop - Custom labs custom skin suit that comes in at \\u00a32,500 / $3,167 with a custom fitting and aero testing included.\", \"from\": 3484, \"to\": 3671, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Other competitors\", \"from\": 3484, \"to\": 3501}, {\"ngram\": \"the Assos offering\", \"from\": 3505, \"to\": 3523}, {\"ngram\": \"the WattShop - Custom labs custom skin suit\", \"from\": 3546, \"to\": 3589}, {\"ngram\": \"a custom\", \"from\": 3628, \"to\": 3636}, {\"ngram\": \"aero testing\", \"from\": 3649, \"to\": 3661}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Santini also offers its Viper skinsuit which is said to be used by Trek Segafredo and the Australia National cycling team, Santini will provide you with a quote if you are interested in one.\", \"from\": 3672, \"to\": 3862, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3744, \"end\": 3753, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Massimo_Zanetti_Beverage_Group\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Segafredo\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Massimo_Zanetti_Beverage_Group\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Massimo_Zanetti_Beverage_Group\"}, {\"begin\": 3762, \"end\": 3771, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 0.9998160975561234, \"rank\": 0.00017967451970610446, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Santini\", \"from\": 3672, \"to\": 3679}, {\"ngram\": \"its Viper skinsuit\", \"from\": 3692, \"to\": 3710}, {\"ngram\": \"Santini\", \"from\": 3795, \"to\": 3802}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We expect to see more equipment from clothing to road and track equipment quietly appear in the run-up to the Paris Olympics.\", \"from\": 3866, \"to\": 3991, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"more equipment\", \"from\": 3883, \"to\": 3897}, {\"ngram\": \"clothing\", \"from\": 3903, \"to\": 3911}, {\"ngram\": \"road and track equipment\", \"from\": 3915, \"to\": 3939}, {\"ngram\": \"the run-up\", \"from\": 3958, \"to\": 3968}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 3972, \"to\": 3990}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As mentioned, some of it is not openly shouted about but we will be doing our best to spot it when it does appear.\", \"from\": 3992, \"to\": 4106, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's always exciting to spot new and cutting-edge equipment in an Olympic year as manufacturers strive to provide athletes with the very best.\", \"from\": 4107, \"to\": 4249, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"new and cutting-edge equipment\", \"from\": 4136, \"to\": 4166}, {\"ngram\": \"an Olympic year\", \"from\": 4170, \"to\": 4185}, {\"ngram\": \"manufacturers\", \"from\": 4189, \"to\": 4202}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 4221, \"to\": 4229}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The track bike narrative in the run-up to Paris 24 has been interesting to follow with a range of outlandish designs appearing as the aero boundaries are pushed.\", \"from\": 4251, \"to\": 4412, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The track bike narrative\", \"from\": 4251, \"to\": 4275}, {\"ngram\": \"the run-up\", \"from\": 4279, \"to\": 4289}, {\"ngram\": \"Paris\", \"from\": 4293, \"to\": 4298}, {\"ngram\": \"a range\", \"from\": 4338, \"to\": 4345}, {\"ngram\": \"outlandish designs\", \"from\": 4349, \"to\": 4367}, {\"ngram\": \"the aero boundaries\", \"from\": 4381, \"to\": 4400}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Thewild-looking Stromm track bikeas well asToot Racing offeringsare just two bikes that have caught the eye so far.\", \"from\": 4413, \"to\": 4528, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Thewild-looking Stromm track bikeas\", \"from\": 4413, \"to\": 4448}, {\"ngram\": \"just two bikes\", \"from\": 4481, \"to\": 4495}, {\"ngram\": \"the eye\", \"from\": 4513, \"to\": 4520}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Tom joined the Cyclingnews team in late 2022 as a tech writer.\", \"from\": 4532, \"to\": 4594, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4547, \"end\": 4558, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cyclingnews.com\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Cyclingnews\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cyclingnews.com\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cyclingnews.com\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Tom\", \"from\": 4532, \"to\": 4535}, {\"ngram\": \"a tech writer\", \"from\": 4580, \"to\": 4593}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Despite having a degree in English Literature he has spent his entire working life in the cycling industry in one form or another.\", \"from\": 4595, \"to\": 4725, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a degree\", \"from\": 4610, \"to\": 4618}, {\"ngram\": \"English Literature\", \"from\": 4622, \"to\": 4640}, {\"ngram\": \"his entire working life\", \"from\": 4654, \"to\": 4677}, {\"ngram\": \"the cycling industry\", \"from\": 4681, \"to\": 4701}, {\"ngram\": \"one form\", \"from\": 4705, \"to\": 4713}, {\"ngram\": \"another\", \"from\": 4717, \"to\": 4724}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He has over 10 years of experience as a qualified mechanic, with the last five years before joining Cyclingnews being spent running an independent workshop.\", \"from\": 4726, \"to\": 4882, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4826, \"end\": 4837, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cyclingnews.com\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Cyclingnews\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cyclingnews.com\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cyclingnews.com\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"over 10 years\", \"from\": 4733, \"to\": 4746}, {\"ngram\": \"experience\", \"from\": 4750, \"to\": 4760}, {\"ngram\": \"a qualified mechanic\", \"from\": 4764, \"to\": 4784}, {\"ngram\": \"the last five years\", \"from\": 4791, \"to\": 4810}, {\"ngram\": \"an independent workshop\", \"from\": 4858, \"to\": 4881}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This means he is just as happy tinkering away in the garage as he is out on the road bike, and he is not afraid to pull a bike apart or get hands-on with it when testing to really see what it's made of.\", \"from\": 4883, \"to\": 5085, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the garage\", \"from\": 4932, \"to\": 4942}, {\"ngram\": \"the road bike\", \"from\": 4959, \"to\": 4972}, {\"ngram\": \"a bike\", \"from\": 5003, \"to\": 5009}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He has ridden and raced bikes from an early age up to a national level on the road and track, and has ridden and competed in most disciplines.\", \"from\": 5089, \"to\": 5231, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"bikes\", \"from\": 5113, \"to\": 5118}, {\"ngram\": \"an early age\", \"from\": 5124, \"to\": 5136}, {\"ngram\": \"a national level\", \"from\": 5143, \"to\": 5159}, {\"ngram\": \"the road\", \"from\": 5163, \"to\": 5171}, {\"ngram\": \"track\", \"from\": 5176, \"to\": 5181}, {\"ngram\": \"most disciplines\", \"from\": 5214, \"to\": 5230}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He has a keen eye for pro-team tech and enjoys spotting new or interesting components in the wild.\", \"from\": 5232, \"to\": 5330, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a keen eye\", \"from\": 5239, \"to\": 5249}, {\"ngram\": \"pro-team tech\", \"from\": 5254, \"to\": 5267}, {\"ngram\": \"new or interesting components\", \"from\": 5288, \"to\": 5317}, {\"ngram\": \"the wild\", \"from\": 532